lead_paragraph: Teenager Lance Stroll will be able to handle the pressure when he makes his debut for Williams as Formula One's latest hotshot next season, according to 1997 world champion Jacques Villeneuve.

headline.print_headline: Stroll Can Handle F1 Pressure: Villeneuve
